On Sat, 2 Sep 1995 m.rubin9@genie.geis.com wrote:

>  
> With Imagine 3.3 I just realized that I could easily shift my screen
> resolution to 800 x 600 via Imagine preferences and my Picasso.
> Pretty cool!
